Name: Add-NetNatExternalAddress
Synopsis: Adds an external address to a NAT instance.

Name: Add-NetNatStaticMapping
Synopsis: Adds a static mapping to a NAT instance.

Name: Get-NetNatExternalAddress
Synopsis: Gets external addresses configured for NAT instances.

Name: Get-NetNatGlobal
Synopsis: Retrieves global settings for all NAT instances on a computer.

Name: Get-NetNatStaticMapping
Synopsis: Gets static mappings configured on NAT instances.

Name: Remove-NetNatExternalAddress
Synopsis: Removes an external address from a NAT instance.

Name: Remove-NetNatStaticMapping
Synopsis: Removes static mappings from a NAT instance.

Name: Set-NetNatGlobal
Synopsis: Modifies global settings for NAT instances on a computer.
